OL,3,CTop PSNI officer brands disgraced ex-
OL,4,Cconstable's actions despicable
OL,6,FPolice have commented for the first
OL,7,Ftime about the sentencing of a corrupt
OL,8,Fofficer in connection with one of the
OL,9,Fmost controversial killings in
OL,10,FNorthern Ireland - the loyalist murder
OL,11,Fof Robert Hamill.
OL,13,FThe actions of an ex-constable who was
OL,14,Fon duty that night and who rang a
OL,15,Fsuspect just hours later have been
OL,16,Fbranded ''despicable''.
OL,18,FLast Friday, former RUC officer Robert
OL,19,FCecil Atkinson was jailed for a year
OL,20,Fafter finally admitting conspiring to
OL,21,Fpervert the course of justice.
