OL,3,CTop PSNI officer brands disgraced ex-
OL,4,Cconstable's actions despicable
OL,6,FHe was one of four officers on duty
OL,7,Fwhen the 25-year-old was attacked by a
OL,8,Floyalist mob in Portadown in April
OL,9,F1997.
OL,11,FBut it was a phonecall made to the
OL,12,Fhome of a young man who became a
OL,13,Fmurder suspect that found him in the
OL,14,Fdock.
OL,16,FFor years he denied doing anything
OL,17,Fwrong and continued to serve as a
OL,18,Fpolice officer before retiring when
OL,19,Fthe RUC became the PSNI.
