OL,6,FIt was only in April this year
OL,7,FAtkinson finally admitted his guilt.
OL,9,FThe judge branding him a disgrace in
OL,10,Funiform, revealing he continued to
OL,11,Fserve as a police officer for years as
OL,12,Fa criminal.
OL,14,FNow police have added their voice to
OL,15,Fthe condemnation.
