OL,3,CTop PSNI officer brands disgraced ex-
OL,4,Cconstable's actions despicable
OL,6,FIn a statement to UTV, Detective Chief
OL,7,FSuperintendent Eamonn Corrigan, Head
OL,8,Fof the PSNI's Serious Crime Branch
OL,9,Fsaid: ''This man's disgraceful actions
OL,10,Ffell far below the standard we expect
OL,11,Ffrom our officers and staff.
OL,13,F''It is clear that Atkinson
OL,14,Fdeliberately misled an investigation
OL,15,Fwhich ultimately became a murder
OL,16,Finquiry whilst continuing to work as a
OL,17,Fpolice officer, this behaviour was
OL,18,Fdespicable and totally unacceptable.
