OL,6,F''We understand that this will
OL,7,Fundoutedly be difficult for the family
OL,8,Fof Robert Hamill and our thoughts are
OL,9,Fwith all of them at what we recognise
OL,10,Fmust be an emotional time.
OL,12,F''We, as a Police Service, will not
OL,13,Ftolerate wrongdoing from any officer
OL,14,For staff and we expect the highest
OL,15,Fstandards and professionalism and
OL,16,Fintegrity from them.''
